(5, 'Shop About Block', 'shop_about_block', '<div class="shop-about clearfix">\r\n<div class="col-1">\r\n<h2>平衡美學</h2>\r\n<div class="text">\r\n<div class="logo"><img src="{{skin url=''images/logo.png''}}" alt="" /></div>\r\n<p>從水、油的恰度調和開始，體現仁光堂為你肌膚綻放的平衡美學。</p>\r\n<p>仁光堂傳承茶花經年的養生智慧，以現代科技提煉茶花籽油，設計迎合不同肌質需要的茶花籽油產品，將茶花籽油的效能發揮極致，體現不過多、不過少的中庸美顏之道，從水、油的恰度調和開始，為你淨化肌膚，活化肌理，這就是專屬仁光堂的平衡美學。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-2 newsletter">\r\n<h3>電郵通訊</h3>\r\n<div class="form-holder"><form action="{{store url=''newsletter/subscriber/new''}}" method="POST"><input type="email" name="email" /> <button type="submit"><span><span>登記</span></span></button></form></div>\r\n<div class="social-buttons">\r\n<a href="https://www.facebook.com/renguangdo" target="_blank"><img src="{{media url="wysiwyg/icon-facebook.png"}}" alt="Facebook" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '2014-02-19 00:23:58', '2014-03-04 02:28:03', 1),
